						               													<description>Lord Shi, a Commander in the Mongolian supremacy that seeks to ravage all of Japan. With his fearsome generals, hordes of soldiers, bandits and assassins, Lord Shi has set his sights on Kojima Island a small and quiet island with plenty of inhabitants that co-exist peacefully until Lord Shi&amp;rsquo;s invasion. Now you must rise up and defeat this tyrant. Rally your fellow villagers, build your equipment, gather your resolve and Battle For Kojima!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You are a leader of one of the many villages around Kojima Island under siege from the Mongolian army. You defend yourself, build your resolve and fight for honour, defeating their forces from the island. You start by assembling a band of villagers willing to brave the hazards ahead and equip them with fearsome weapons. Once prepared, you will lead them into peril, cutting down their forces, defeat the generals, and slay the elusive Lord Shi!&amp;nbsp;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player constructs a custom deck of cards during the game. Your deck represents the capabilities and resources of your adventuring party. At the end of each turn, you discard your entire hand and draw a new one, thus it is imperative to create a deck that is reliable&amp;nbsp;and powerful. How well you use the strengths and powers of your cards determines whether victory will be yours!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On Your Turn you can either:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- Attack an enemy&amp;#10;- Gather Equipment or Villagers&amp;#10;- Rally by discarding weaker cards for stronger ones&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each card has a certain ammount of Victory Points (VP) and the Aim is to get as many VP before the game ends. The game ends when Lord Shi is defeated.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
